packed layout record Word:
  value: u16

read word checked bytes: view of u8 gives i32:
  require length of bytes is greater than or equal to size of Word
  let word be read Word from bytes at 0
  word.value as i32

main gives i32:
  let bytes be buffer of 2 u8 filled with 0
  bytes at 0 becomes 42
  read word checked bytes
